==Title==
I have moved this material to "IFTC Jump into English Textbook - Teacher's Manual". It was called "IFTC Jump into English Textbook (Teacher's Manual)" some time ago before it was moved to "ESL/EFL Lesson Plans/IFTC Jump into English Textbook (Teacher's Manual)". From what I have understood from the Wikibooks policy, the titles of books should not use the larger subject in their title. Thus, if the title of the book is BT, and the larger subject is LS, the title of the book should be "BT" and not "LS/BT". If the first chapter is titled "CH1", its title in the Wikibooks should be "BT/CH1". --[[User:Dan Polansky|Dan Polansky]] ([[User talk:Dan Polansky|talk]]) 12:26, 8 March 2009 (UTC)

